<span class="line"><span style="color:#7F848E;font-style:italic;">The parent should send a byte to the child; the child should print &quot;&lt;pid&gt;: received ping&quot;, where &lt;pid&gt; is its process ID, write the byte on the pipe to the parent, and exit;</span></span>
